## 16. Widget Input Handling (Special Cases)

For widgets that need to detect which button was clicked:

```cpp
void OnRelicButtonClicked()
{
    for (const auto& Pair : ButtonToRelicIndexMap)
    {
        if (Pair.Key && Pair.Key->IsHovered())  // Check which button is hovered
        {
            SelectedRelicIndex = Pair.Value;
            RefreshDetailPanel();
            return;
        }
    }
}
